{"tid":47104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[地獄鬼國]豆腐渣？男童一推開　玻璃門粉碎","createTime":"2016-12-20T06:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T12:26:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8df82a1d4afe749ba64dcce6d23fd383c70e6aa5","tid":47104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161220/photo/bkncn-20161220080022721-1220_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161220104714\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161220%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161220080022721-1220_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161220104714&h=f972872e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=m%2Fae%2Fr5VMBUDgVt2IB%2BLYAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f3b7f46c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 內地的建築質量屢屢惹人詬病，四川眉山市仁壽縣前日更出現恐怖一幕，一名男童推開商舖一道玻璃門時，整塊玻璃門突然碎裂並倒塌，門框及大堆玻璃碎直接砸向男童頭部，受傷男童需送院救治。對此，網民紛紛怒斥：「看吧！又是豆腐渣」、「絕對要追究，這個不能忍！」<br />\n<br />\n據網傳片段可見，當日下午5時許，一名男童進入仁壽縣「美加好」商場地下一間店舖時，慘遭無故倒塌的玻璃門砸傷，同行男女隨即將他抱走送院。<br />\n<br />\n事件惹起網民憤慨，不少網民指責：「甚麼破玻璃！說倒便倒？」「這個不能忍，都將老百姓的性命安全當成甚麼了？」也有網民慨嘆：「出個門都要提心吊膽，這個社會也太悲哀。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161220/bkncn-20161220080022721-1220_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161220%2Fbkncn-20161220080022721-1220_05011_001.html&d=m%2Fae%2Fr5VMBUDgVt2IB%2BLYAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8f8e69c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161220/bkncn-20161220080022721-1220_05011_001.html</a><br />\n原文有片"},{"pid":"478085ad3e7543649474a51e76b07488a9183eca","tid":47104,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"力拔山兮。。"},{"pid":"850f6288e91424c95b712dbf4a49f28dc62cd4d0","tid":47104,"uid":54470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"乜強國人今日先知有豆腐渣工程咩?做乜講到咁出奇咁"},{"pid":"6faa0e62735691f9958d70300c625745d254aa03","tid":47104,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"可能係個細路好大力呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c6a477b12b518e923273bcf6138c642272d890","tid":47104,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1591b63a87e53d3c5cf42358e09550ca53fda2b2","tid":47104,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"根本細路問題 支那不存在什麼豆腐渣工程 <br />\n百姓不得說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3a100746eaa859bcb8380916a8f6e133beb35a","tid":47104,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"可能係個細路天生神力呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a3cc4f75b6b2ca610c9c745cca997d8857847d","tid":47104,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"少年項羽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ca826698a7c4378c3f8d9012a30e18d150dbf8","tid":47104,"uid":8575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"個老母多得個𡃁仔唔少<br />\n又要賠錢"},{"pid":"b08f23361bd04a28ef9e4debc345ca38b859f2a3","tid":47104,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"生有神力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62f21813f2bdc4b15bba5a066b2564c3e8078cd","tid":47104,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"老闆： 咁大力做乜春呀？！ 賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb11947a8126a088f6fbba185abe59593048666","tid":47104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a